title: Petros Dourdoubakis - 2 Albums More (Greek Music)@320
description:
1. Petros Dourdoumpakis - Apo Oneiro Se Oneiro


To 1994 o Petros Dourdoumpakis dimiourgei ena disko "oneiremeno". Edo sunantame monadika ti Melina Kana stis "Tufles Elpides", ton Petro Dourdoumpaki sto "Oti anapse tha svisei" kai sto "Apo oneiro se oneiro", eno summetehoun episis oi Kostas Paulidis kai Katia Papadopoulou.
Ton suntheti plaisionoun exairetoi mousikoi eno to exofullo tou diskou kosmei to ergo tou Gianni Tsarouhi "endumiwn" ladi se pani, 1975, apo tin idiwtiki sullogi tou Idrumatos Gianni Tsarouhi. (musical.gr)
